{
  "name": "RPlog_Complicated_Motivations",
  "title": "Complicated Motivations at the Coronation",
  "summary": "At a lavish coronation gala high above ruined Selene, the newly-crowned Imperator Tyler Damion holds court among Moffs and military brass while his alchemical Wookiee bodyguard Sentinel looms nearby. The Falleen crimelord Nasiri attends to observe and perhaps profit, the Sarian Admiral Crestian Tarasar quietly works the room as Caspar's representative, and Damion's bitter Jedi sister Johanna arrives barely concealing her contempt, ostensibly only to bring her son Etiel home. A sharp confrontation erupts when Damion dismisses the value of profit, prompting Johanna to throw his reliance on her fortune in his face; her rage nearly boils into violence until her son Etiel defuses it. Damion apologizes, and the gala's politics resume: Crestian announces Caspar's new constitution and impending return home, while the businesswoman Elana Tracer is abruptly appointed Moff of Selene and tasked with renegotiating the embezzler Oppenheimer's CSA charter, before the Imperator departs to inspect his command ship.",
